headline: Three Reasons to Avoid FAST and One Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Fastenal’s 15.9% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 5.6%, and its stock price has climbed to $74.70 per share. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
